    <exercise>
      <statement>
        <p>
          What are the converse and inverse of <q>If you watch my back, I'll
          watch your back.</q>?
        </p>
      </statement>
      <hint>
        <p>
          The converse is <q>If I watch your back, then you'll watch my back.</q> (Sounds a little dopey doesn't it <mdash /> likes its sort of a wishful thinking<ellipsis />)
